.\" Man page for btrfs-backup-ng list
.TH BTRFS-BACKUP-NG-LIST 1 "January 2026" "btrfs-backup-ng" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
btrfs-backup-ng-list \- show snapshots and backups
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B btrfs-backup-ng list
[\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
List all snapshots across configured volumes and their backup targets.
Shows snapshot names, timestamps, and locations.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-\-volume " PATH"
Only list snapshots for the specified volume(s). Can be specified multiple times.
.TP
.B \-\-json
Output in JSON format for scripting and automation.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
List all snapshots:
.B btrfs-backup-ng list
.TP
List snapshots for specific volume:
.B btrfs-backup-ng list --volume /home
.TP
Output as JSON:
.B btrfs-backup-ng list --json
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR btrfs-backup-ng (1),
.BR btrfs-backup-ng-status (1)
